org.universAAL.ui.dm.dialogManagement

Class DialogPriorityQueue

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.universAAL.ui.dm.dialogManagement.DialogPriorityQueue
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IUIRequestPool
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    NonRedundantDialogPriorityQueue

    public class DialogPriorityQueue
extends Object
implements IUIRequestPool
    This IUIRequestPool will manage active dialogs in a PriorityQueue while keeping suspended dialogs in a Map.
    Author:
    amedrano
